  Consistent Characters & Styles

In this video, we'll take a look at how to create consistent characters (& styles) inside Midjourney. The process of creating consistent characters has never been easier. By using the Character Reference feature you can unlock a creative superpower and tell stories with characters that stay the same throughout. It's an amazing feature and I'm excited to explore it with you today!

  • Link to Assets

Codes Used:

  • --cref (image link)
  • --cw (0-100)
    • 0 = Inconsistent Clothing and Accessories
    • 100 = Consistent Clothing and Accessories
  • --sref (image link)
  • --sw (0-1000, 100 is default)
